<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Information is not available on a fire regime for this alliance. Areas with the <i>Cylindropuntia bigelovii </i>alliance have burned, including stands in Hellhole Canyon of Anza-Borrego Desert State Park (Chester and Madore 2005).</div>
